parameters.name: Charlotte
parameters.teaser: 7 month old girl who presents with bilious vomiting and no bowel movements in 36 hours
parameters.clinical_descrip: 7 m/o girl who was healthy until the day before admission when she developed bilious vomiting.  No bowel movement for 36 hours.  Temperature 99. Pulse 120. She is irritable but consolable and seems to be having episodic abdominal pain. Her abdomen is mildly distended.
